42:04.523 --> 42:07.957
<i> MR. PRITCHARD?!</i>
<i> MR. PRITCHARD?!</i>

42:15.667 --> 42:17.734
<i> [ Normal voice ]</i>
<i> MR. PRITCHARD?!</i>

42:17.736 --> 42:20.336
<i> MR. PRITCHARD?!</i>

42:20.338 --> 42:22.171
[ BLADES WHIRRING ]

42:22.173 --> 42:23.640
WHAT IS...

42:23.642 --> 42:25.108
WHAT IS THAT?

42:26.845 --> 42:28.978
<i> PROTOTYPE LOOKING GLASS.</i>

42:28.980 --> 42:30.747
<i> U.A.V. RESCUE.</i>

42:32.717 --> 42:35.218
CAN YOU OPEN THE DOOR
AND REACH FOR THE STRAPS?

42:37.422 --> 42:42.058
<i> MR. PRITCHARD,</i>
<i> CAN YOU OPEN THE DOOR FOR ME?</i>

42:42.060 --> 42:44.327
<i> GOOD.</i>

42:44.329 --> 42:49.232
¶¶

42:49.234 --> 42:52.335
<i> ARRESTS WERE MADE TODAY</i>
<i> TYING UPPER-LEVEL FBI AGENTS</i>

42:52.337 --> 42:54.837
<i> TO A SERIES</i>
<i> OF LOCAL BANK ROBBERIES.</i>

42:54.839 --> 42:56.873
Man: WE APPRECIATE
YOUR DIFFICULTY IN TURNING IN

42:56.875 --> 42:58.174
YOUR PARTNER AND BOSS.

42:58.176 --> 43:00.343
YOUR WORK HAS ALLOWED US
TO CLEAR THE BANK ROBBERIES,

43:00.345 --> 43:02.845
AS WELL AS UNCOVER CORRUPTION
IN THE BUREAU.

43:02.847 --> 43:05.515
BUT THIS HEARING FOCUSES
SOLELY ON THE EVENTS

43:05.517 --> 43:06.683
ON THE LIBERTY BRIDGE,

43:06.685 --> 43:10.386
SO PLEASE TELL THIS PANEL
EXACTLY WHAT YOU SAW.

43:10.388 --> 43:13.222
WHAT HAPPENED WAS, WE FOUGHT.

43:13.224 --> 43:16.059
I USED A TIRE IRON
TO RENDER KERNIE

43:16.061 --> 43:18.461
AND MY PARTNER UNCONSCIOUS.

43:18.463 --> 43:22.198
THERE WERE ONLY THE THREE OF US
ON THE BRIDGE THAT NIGHT.

43:28.974 --> 43:31.608
¶¶

43:45.957 --> 43:48.858
ARTHUR, ZOOM IN ON MARY.

43:52.831 --> 43:54.664
I DON'T KNOW WHAT FACE THAT IS.

43:54.666 --> 43:57.367
<i> Arthur: I BELIEVE THOSE</i>
<i> FEATURES REPRESENT LONGING.</i>

44:04.009 --> 44:05.842
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

44:21.493 --> 44:24.293
<i> I STAND HERE</i>
<i> ACCUSED OF CORRUPTION,</i>

44:24.295 --> 44:27.463
<i> WITNESS INTIMIDATION,</i>
<i> BRUTALITY.</i>

44:27.465 --> 44:30.466
<i> [ Distorted ]</i>
<i> I CONFESS TO DOING MY JOB.</i>

44:30.468 --> 44:31.834
Younger Jimmy: I CONFESS

44:31.836 --> 44:34.370
TO KEEPING THIS TOWN'S PEACE.

44:40.045 --> 44:42.945
Mary:
DO YOU KNOW WHO YOU ARE?

44:46.217 --> 44:47.316
[ SIGHS ]

44:47.318 --> 44:52.121
YEAH, MISS GOODWIN,
I SURE DO.

44:52.123 --> 44:55.091
I'M SHERIFF JIMMY PRITCHARD.

